OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of showery
OL,8,Frain, heavy at times. Chance of a few
OL,9,Fclearer spells developing towards
OL,10,Fmorning. Windy at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FWindy as cloud and rain
OL,13,Fspread east through the morning, heavy
OL,14,Fat times. Clear spells and scattered,
OL,15,Fblustery showers through the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
