OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain on Friday morning, becoming
OL,7,Fbrighter with a few showers later.
OL,8,FBright Saturday morning, before rain
OL,9,Fspreads east later. Cloudy and breezy
OL,10,Fwith outbreaks of rain on Sunday.
